reviews.review_text: Great Show! This was my second show, I was still in the navy when a friend gave me the ticket for this show.Even though i attended the show alone i still felt as though I was among fiends, thats the beauty of bieng at a dead show.About half way into 2nd set was I suddenly pushed backward, as regained my composure another man in chinese dress was spraying a fire extinquiser into the air. As the smoke plume cleared a 40 foot oriental dragon danced thru the croud, tied to his tail was spining dancer in a tiger costume.Needless to say I was completely blown away. Thanks for the trip down memory lane, it was a great show. M
ex rec, pg show Excellent recording. PG show, with some very nice moments, and also some slips and drops.
